            <title>[FLINK-8557] OperatorSubtaskDescriptionText causes failures on Windows</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-8557</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;File-based state backends that use the description provided by &lt;tt&gt;OperatorSubtaskDescriptionText&lt;/tt&gt; for file names will categorically fail on Windows as they contain characters that aren&apos;t allowed in paths &quot;(&quot;, &quot;)&quot; and &quot;/&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
